
              <div class='row'>
                <div class='col-sm-12'>
                  <div class='page-header'>
                    <h1 class='pull-left'>
                      <i class='icon-user'></i>
                      <span>用户个人信息</span>
                    </h1>
                    <div class='pull-right'>
                      <ul class='breadcrumb'>
                        <li>
                          <a href='index.html'>
                            <i class='icon-bar-chart'></i>
                          </a>
                        </li>
                        <li class='separator'>
                          <i class='icon-angle-right'></i>
                        </li>
                        <li>Example pages</li>
                        <li class='separator'>
                          <i class='icon-angle-right'></i>
                        </li>
                        <li class='active'>User profile</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class='row'>
                <div class='col-sm-3 col-lg-2'>
                  <div class='box'>
                    <div class='box-content'>
                      <img class="img-responsive" src="http://placehold.it/230x230&amp;text=Photo" />
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class='col-sm-9 col-lg-10'>
                  <div class='box'>
                    <div class='box-content box-double-padding'>
                      <form class='form' style='margin-bottom: 0;'>
                      <%= form_for(@user, url: kobe_users_path, method: :patch, html: {class: "form form-horizontal validate-form", style: "margin-bottom: 0;"}) do |u| %>
                        <fieldset>
                          <div class='col-sm-4'>
                            <div class='lead'>
                              <i class='icon-github text-contrast'></i>
                              账户信息
                            </div>
                            <small class='text-muted'><p>为了方便接受本站的推送信息，请使用常用的邮箱地址。当您忘记了登录密码时可以通过该邮箱重置。如果您变更了邮箱地址，系统会给您发送一份激活邮件，请到邮箱激活即可。</p></small>
                          </div>
                          <div class='col-sm-7 col-sm-offset-1'>
                            <div class='form-group'>
                              <label>E-mail地址</label>
                              <input class='form-control' id='email' name="user[email]" data-rule-email='true' data-rule-required='true' placeholder='E-mail地址' type='text' />
                            </div>
                            <hr class='hr-normal'>
                            <div class='form-group'>
                              <div class='controls'>
                                <div class='checkbox'>
                                  <label>
                                    <input data-target='#change-password' data-toggle='collapse' id='changepasswordcheck' type='checkbox' value='option1' />
                                    修改密码?
                                  </label>
                                </div>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class='collapse' id='change-password'>
                              <div class='form-group'>
                                <label>密码</label>
                                <input class='form-control' id='password' name="user[password]" data-rule-minlength='6' data-rule-password='true' placeholder='密码' type='password' />
                              </div>
                              <div class='form-group'>
                                <label>请再次输入密码</label>
                                <input class='form-control' id='password-confirmation' name='password_confirmation' data-rule-equalto='#password' placeholder='请再次输入密码' type='password' />
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </fieldset>
                        <hr class='hr-normal'>
                        <fieldset>
                          <div class='col-sm-4'>
                            <div class='lead'>
                              <i class='icon-user text-contrast'></i>
                              个人资料
                            </div>
                            <small class='text-muted'><p>默认情况下，您的个人信息仅对系统内的其他成员可见，如果您不希望别人看到您的个人信息，您可以选择“信息保密”，目前保密的内容仅限于“身份证号码”和“手机号码”。</p></small>
                          </div>
                          <div class='col-sm-7 col-sm-offset-1'>
                            <div class='form-group'>
                              <label class='controls'>姓名</label>
                              <input class='form-control' id='name' name="user[name]" data-rule-required='true' placeholder='姓名' type='text' />
                            </div>
                            <div class='form-group'>
                              <label class='controls'>性别</label>
                              <input class='form-control' id='gender' name="user[name]" data-rule-maxlength='1' data-rule-required='true' placeholder='性别' type='text' />
                            </div>
                            <div class='form-group'>
                              <label>出生日期</label>
                              <input class='form-control' id='lastname' placeholder='Last name' type='text'>
                            </div>
                            <hr class='hr-normal'>
                            <div class='form-group'>
                              <label>个人简历</label>
                              <textarea class='autosize form-control' id='bio' placeholder='Bio'></textarea>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </fieldset>
                        <div class='form-actions form-actions-padding' style='margin-bottom: 0;'>
                          <div class='text-right'>
                            <div class='btn btn-primary btn-lg'>
                              <i class='icon-save'></i>
                              Save
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      <% end %>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>